{"type": "article", "id": 33034, "title": "在家里放上这朵云，它能帮你放音乐｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-08T23:08:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 19566, "name": "Note Design Studio"}, {"id": 33688, "name": "Richard Clarkson Studio"}, {"id": 33689, "name": "桃太郎JEANS"}, {"id": 33690, "name": "Paper Up"}, {"id": 33691, "name": "høly"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 33692, "name": "Crealev"}, {"id": 33693, "name": "Japan Tobacco"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 245, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161009070333JmXTkN7BaCqR3IgO.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Making Weather by Richard Clarkson Studio &amp; Crealev</h3><p>你有没有幻想过听到一朵云发出音乐？设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Richard Clarkson</a> 和专攻悬浮科技的公司 <a href=\"http://www.crealev.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Crealev</a> 最近联手打造了一款名为 Making Weather 的设备，与底座通过磁性形成悬浮效果的是一个用涤纶纤维制成的云朵，内置了蓝牙扬声器以及 LED 灯。云朵不仅会小幅度地上下浮动、进行 360 度旋转，配合能营造出雷电效果的 LED 灯以及底座顶部的镜面，放在室内显得相当别致。每一个云朵都采用手工填充，因此它们的造型也是独一无二的。目前 Making Weather 尚处于原型阶段，设计团队希望它最终能够实现量产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213837blijx7eaMyKtEThA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213837tRWL1KPic7IZGQ0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610082138373I08764pUiCGnjWw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610082138389fU0HWMC3s4JZloN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213838usTOzxWSagfjJb2q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016100821383824oQibPt8ODaXzLk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fugue Series by Note Design Studio</h3><p>          </p><p>来自瑞典的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://notedesignstudio.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Note</a> 以赋格曲（fugue）为灵感为<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>打造了同名的赋格系列，这款底部附有橡木柜腿的金属柜就是系列的第一件作品。柜腿采用稳固的三角型设计，不仅提供了有效的力学支撑之外，还兼顾到线条的优美。上方的金属柜因此也不再是无趣地伫立着，看起来更加轻巧。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300140\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1710 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610082201243gBGoh0UERie27xD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008220125u8HABRGwzTyKcbCf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008220124lGUtPcJgKX7ZI4RY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008220125eg4cIrQPsRFqUVlN.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008220124PgUSDWqm05FnZtx4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008220124xdFC6lc5kL7vwGuK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3><br></h3><h3>DOME+ by Rita Koralevics</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你喜欢回收材料所特有的粗糙感，不妨来看看匈牙利手工制品品牌 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/paperupcollection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paper Up</a> 最新推出的这款名为 DOME+ 的灯具。Paper Up 由设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/ritakoralevics\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rita Koralevics</a> 在 2012 年创立，产品的一个特色就是它们都含有 100% 的回收纸，而 DOME+ 也不例外：它的灯罩融合了纸与混凝土两种材料制成，并且配有一个竹制把手，延续了品牌的环保理念。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.kabelfabrik.at/product/paper-up-dome/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 80 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008233407wtfg1dkHNKVpzL6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610082334072pGR6zHfdMQXB5tJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008233408Cd3hTtfsJjqngV7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008233408EMKfQ4NhUqbXsdLD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008233408cBlPNajiIRnVKxfk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008233409n8pYWP5SUDzcXHiR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.237500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FEND by FEND</h3><p>你是不是因为觉得自行车头盔不够美观而且携带起来又不方便，宁愿选择不戴直接上路呢？来自美国的设计团队 FEND 带来的这款折叠式头盔或许能够让你不再那么抗拒戴头盔这件事了，聚拢后它能缩小到原体积的 1/3，携带起来方便不少。完全展开后它会自动锁定大小，当中镂空的结构刚好可以缓解使用时的闷热感。FEND 由 EPP 聚合物制作而成，这种材料有着十分优异的抗震吸能性，而且质量相当轻。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fendhelmet/fend-the-collapsible-bicycle-helmet\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008214114Tjef5740lXFDHiWR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008214112ZhKou7rTQFfV4BMb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008214115nVEqUk5eLgT8oXPm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008214114RAbpXL1Cfg7VWDIU.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008214113n20t5YLhCpSUsFry.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.836765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PURO by høly</h3><p>在 2013 年雅典的 48 小时设计马拉松（<a href=\"http://designathon.gr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designathon</a>）上，设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.holy.gd/\" rel=\"nofollow\">høly</a> 的任务是为瓶装水概念品牌 PURO <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/8309597/PURO-Premium-Water\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计形象</a>。三年后，høly 在旧作的基础上<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43029981/PURO-Re-imagined\" rel=\"nofollow\">又重新进行了一番设计</a>：运用在静态水包装上的木塞设计不仅被延续了下来，对应的带有颗粒质感的棕色也被运用到了配套的周边物品上。为了更好地表现出水的纯净，除了简洁的特殊符号以外，新版还加入了北欧风景作为视觉元素，出现在纸盒以及包裹着水瓶的薄纸上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213755TKmFV9r35MYUdB4q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213756tesPVSnaBoIz6DCH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213755H1kfU8O9pzGxDcXq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610082137561m0byieRLpsIkAgj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213756SWzPQ2sTRhAoi8Bj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161008213755P9m6dxNnWszKgMS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}